headline: CORE Sells Shoppes of South Semoran in Orlando Retail Market
summary: ORLANDO, Fla., August 12, 2025--CORE SEMORAN, an affiliate of Core Investment Management (CORE), a Miami-based private investor specializing in retail properties across Florida's primary markets, is pleased to announce the successful sale of Shoppes of South Semoran, a 101,000-square-foot retail plaza in Orlando, Florida, for $24 million.
